By":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T01:10:06.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"b866f931cc8398f38f4a6f605a8494c00c83420f","tid":565148,"uid":13878,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T01:21:36.000Z","msg":"完左?"},{"pid":"9613939e6b4d5e16f707fb0b7c22b589cc2ed228","tid":565148,"uid":146707,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T01:27:22.000Z","msg":"吹水台見到 入黎先知故黎<br />\n仲諗住好多文睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes10.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/yipes10.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"644fc35c2393d89d2068d9dfc52b8a1db457f608","tid":565148,"uid":4559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T03:52:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d69d2e77f1b532859e4ad5fffbcdfaa41edb917e","tid":565148,"uid":38707,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T18:02:57.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"f856d12b4ae6ab0dfb5124924358b8538b3e0f61","tid":565148,"uid":61462,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T19:44:37.000Z","msg":"5!d"},{"pid":"020ee03800f7df829b6e3f0abcc11e1054e12a71","tid":565148,"uid":39646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T13:03:12.000Z","msg":"樓豬已死"},{"pid":"7b7e89c63f23544bb7c130cf75cf78bb0fda1145","tid":565148,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T13:09:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa2541adabf168bbd9df73c5711d181573bdbaa","tid":565148,"uid":168161,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-01T13:20:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7882407d476254960385bc9973fcfb76102c0d11","tid":565148,"uid":59984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-06T03:39:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9264b494d6ec45b31254969244894df9237fea52","tid":565148,"uid":71740,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T08:57:17.000Z","msg":"文呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3c2cc638a5b68a2b0f589a810c09a9e8887ecd1","tid":565148,"uid":74277,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T10:33:16.000Z","msg":"「是怎麼了？」溫柔既佢問到，<br />\n<br />\n「嘛，這件事就不提吧，反正都是死人了。」我把雙腳翹起在檯上。<br />\n<br />\n她低下頭，似是疑非思考著，<br />\n<br />\n我沏好了茶，將斟滿了的紫砂茶杯遞給她。<br />\n<br />\n「謝謝⋯」她拿起茶，細細品嚐起來。<br />\n<br />\n「哥哥你真是個好人呢。」<br />\n<br />\n「這話怎說？」<br />\n<br />\n「因為⋯明明我可以任由你處置，你卻對我這麼好。」<br />\n<br />\n「呵呵⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n「哥哥的女朋友的話應該很幸福吧，又有錢，又可靠。」<br />\n<br />\n「我沒有女朋友。」<br />\n<br />\n「怎麼會！」<br />\n<br />\n「嘛，依偎的對象並不是沒有的，只是性質不同吧。」<br />\n<br />\n「那些女孩，也可稱做性奴吧，她們⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n我支吾其詞，按耐住自己的嘴巴，不能將那件事說出！<br />\n<br />\n少女仿佛感受到周圍的氣場，四周充滿著濃烈的黑暗氣息，茶杯的蒸汽在散發著，瞬間變成黑色。<br />\n<br />\n就是這種絕望的感覺，很吸引，我那惡劣至極的嗜好久違地發作了，我猙獰地大笑著，檯面的茶也因我的聲音而震跌。<br />\n<br />\n看著如斯可怕的情境，少女全身震抖著，雙手似乎不受控制地抓緊裙子，壓制著自己的恐懼，她的眼睛無神地凝視著我，如小狗般向我求饒，額頭的汗已令她完全濕透，乃至那幼細的白腿。<br />\n<br />\n此刻，她終於感受到那種生不如死的絕望，如果可以掙扎的話，她老早便做了，如今的她，除了求饒以外，甚麼也做不了。<br />\n<br />\n我張開口，説道：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「她們⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「她們全都⋯⋯」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「死了！」</span></span>"},{"pid":"65922063a845e49b2f49f158be2538f6c72fe584","tid":565148,"uid":143380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-08T10:49:30.000Z","msg":"哦"}]}